{"tid":1204013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我都出，你？","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:03:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T21:45:28.000Z","uid":1693,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ef3698cbc1e19650e5d318647e440927ddc9183","tid":1204013,"uid":1693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"我本來都鍾意少出聲多做事<br />\n但係諗返起當初前一個台(膠登）抗爭自由<br />\n希望多啲人知道 其實大家都做緊嘢<br />\n<br />\n希望去唔到嘅你唔緊要，最緊要有心<br />\n嗰班做嘢嗰班我都睇到 我心裏面真係。。有啲想喊<br />\n我部printer機都玩到就快冇晒墨 要做嘅我都可以做<br />\n啱啱貼野 我元朗朗屏去到天水圍。。絲帶我都排晒<br />\n仆佢個街咁啱又落大雨 個頭濕撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天水圍西鐵站我啱啱俾人查袋 屌佢老母<br />\n<br />\n各位今次唔好輸呀  please !"},{"pid":"efbae8447257d01025f086524105b4d325552aff","tid":1204013,"uid":1693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:08:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bed0d7785fb05cca472addf881d9f2c8b53f9aa","tid":1204013,"uid":1693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:14:01.000Z","msg":"我而家真係好撚憤怒啊 <br />\n你哋12號嘅就12號見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297d1e3e945e3830fc390e5f4d4c5e06701b82da","tid":1204013,"uid":133319,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"茄寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a122ef4578f1b3b1ca1d8268c5578140a25ca2c","tid":1204013,"uid":1693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/11/221500_a0dbb4f84f43f07bb6422f083fa6f48a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F11%2F221500_a0dbb4f84f43f07bb6422f083fa6f48a.png&h=b75f33f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad01031dcd610a695a06861d97974de794490f9e","tid":